events.name: Michigan Wolverines at Florida State Seminoles

headlines.description: Deondre Francois threw a 12-yard touchdown pass to Nyquan Murray with 36 seconds remaining, and No. 10 Florida State beat No. 6 Michigan 33-32 in a wild Orange Bowl on Friday night.
headlines.shortLinkText: No. 10 FSU wins wild Orange Bowl over No. 6 Michigan, 33-32

video.headline: Florida State prevails to stop Michigan in Orange Bowl

events.name: Stanford Cardinal at North Carolina Tar Heels

headlines.description: Bryce Love took over for the absent Christian McCaffrey in the Stanford backfield, running for 119 yards and catching a 49-yard touchdown pass to help the No. 16 Cardinal beat North Carolina 25-2
headlines.shortLinkText: No. 16 Stanford holds off North Carolina 25-23 in Sun Bowl

notes.headline: FRANKLIN AMERICAN MORTGAGE MUSIC CITY BOWL

headlines.description: Joshua Dobbs ran for three touchdowns and 118 yards and threw for 291 yards and another score and Tennessee beat No. 24 Nebraska 38-24 on Friday in the Music City Bowl.
headlines.shortLinkText: Tennessee beats No. 24 Nebraska 38-24 in Music City Bowl

events.name: Georgia Bulldogs at TCU Horned Frogs

headlines.description: Nick Chubb ran for 142 yards and a touchdown Friday as Georgia beat TCU 31-23 in the Liberty Bowl to win a bowl game for the third straight year.
headlines.shortLinkText: Georgia rallies to beat TCU 31-23 in Liberty Bowl

events.name: South Alabama Jaguars at Air Force Falcons

headlines.description: Arion Worthman threw for 207 yards to balance out Air Force's run-heavy offense, Jacobi Owens scored two touchdowns and the Falcons overcame a sluggish start to beat South Alabama 45-21 in Arizon
headlines.shortLinkText: Air Force beats South Alabama 45-21 in Arizona Bowl
